animeTitle: Seitokai no Ichizon Lv.2: Watasu Seitokai
animeDescription: An OVA bundled with the eighth volume of the Seitokai Series Spinoff novel.   The story itself takes place on Valentine's Day where you could see how the second season's heroines handle the awkward situation of giving a gift to the main character, Sugisaki Ken.
